<section class="hero">
  <div class="container flow">
    <div class="hero__content flow">
      <h1 class="section-title text-gradient">
        Hey there, welcome aboard my blog!
      </h1>
      <p>
        In this space, I document my journey in web development with bite-sized
        blogs.
      </p>
